QuestData.Title: Mullby's Marker
QuestData.Description: The Marker looks like it might be important to this Mulby fellow. Returning it to him in Maldraxxus might net you a finder's fee.
QuestData.LogDescription: Return the marker to the Challenger's Promenade in Maldraxxus.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Marcel Mullby at the Challenger's Promenade in Maldraxxus.
